dia.org/resource/Lille\"}, {\"begin\": 1250, \"end\": 1258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bordeaux\", \"score\": 0.9999906490075514, \"rank\": 9.3509735707547e-06, \"text\": \"Bordeaux\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bordeaux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bordeaux\"}, {\"begin\": 1276, \"end\": 1286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strasbourg\", \"score\": 0.9996680981024678, \"rank\": 0.0003320120911193964, \"text\": \"Strasbourg\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strasbourg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strasbourg\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"incidents signal boxes\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"the lines\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1197}, {\"ngram\": \"cities\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"the north\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"the west\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1270}, {\"ngram\": \"the east\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The report quoted two security sources as saying that the modus operandi led to suspicions on leftist militants or environmental activists.\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The report\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1311}, {\"ngram\": \"two security sources\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1339}, {\"ngram\": \"the modus operandi\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"suspicions\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1391}, {\"ngram\": \"leftist militants\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1412}, {\"ngram\": \"environmental activists\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The sources, however, said that there was no evidence yet for the same.\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1512, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The sources\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1452}, {\"ngram\": \"no evidence\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rains spoil the opening ceremony French weather service had predicted that \\\"flooding rains\\\" will occur on Friday and coincide with the Olympics opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1548, \"end\": 1554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.7668489851320619, \"rank\": 0.29041808925894774, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rains\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1519}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1546}, {\"ngram\": \"flooding rains\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1604}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1626}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The prediction did not prove to be wrong as sporadic rainfall kept spattering the ceremony even as spectators largely remain put to witness what some called once-in-a-lifetime spectacle in Paris.\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1873, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1867, \"end\": 1872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0032141997268009e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The prediction\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1692}, {\"ngram\": \"sporadic rainfall\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1739}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1768}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"a-lifetime\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1853}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Associated Press reported that skies above Paris were grey with intermittent drizzle throughout the afternoon but they cleared as the ceremony began but the showers picked up soon just as the procession began advancing the Seine River.\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 2113, \"entiti