howers.\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2284, \"end\": 2286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999999240572, \"rank\": 5.6680483219543453e-11, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mood\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"the spectators\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2350}, {\"ngram\": \"the rain\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2367}, {\"ngram\": \"a small trickle\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2397}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2423}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2452}, {\"ngram\": \"the showers\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ticketing snag and long queues add to spectators' woes Thousands of spectators faced long queues and ticketing problems upon their arrival in Paris for the opening ceremony, according to AFP.\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2632, \"end\": 2637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0032141997268009e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2677, \"end\": 2680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.606119949666664e-14, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"snag\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2503}, {\"ngram\": \"long queues\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2519}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators' woes\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2543}, {\"ngram\": \"Thousands\", \"from\": 2544, \"to\": 2553}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2567}, {\"ngram\": \"long queues\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2585}, {\"ngram\": \"problems\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2608}, {\"ngram\": \"their arrival\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2627}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The agency reported that many gates opened an hour late and two gates opened at least two hours late because concerned staffers had not been delivered scanners to check tickets.\", \"from\": 2683, \"to\": 2860, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The agency\", \"from\": 2683, \"to\": 2693}, {\"ngram\": \"many gates\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2718}, {\"ngram\": \"two gates\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2752}, {\"ngram\": \"concerned staffers\", \"from\": 2792, \"to\": 2810}, {\"ngram\": \"scanners\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2842}, {\"ngram\": \"tickets\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2859}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The police have been amazing, but the organisation sucks,\\\" said German film producer Michael Ohoven, 48, to the agency.\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 2982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2927, \"end\": 2933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"score\": 0.9905795125910589, \"rank\": 0.008553778914837001, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\"}, {\"begin\": 2948, \"end\": 2962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Ohoven\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michael Ohoven\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Ohoven\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Ohoven\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The police\", \"from\": 2863, \"to\": 2873}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisation\", \"from\": 2897, \"to\": 2913}, {\"ngram\": \"the agency\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 2981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ohoven told the agency that he had been waiting an hour in front of a closed gate.\", \"from\": 2984, \"to\": 3066, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ohoven\", \"from\": 2984, \"to\": 2990}, {\"ngram\": \"the agency\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3006}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 3043, \"to\": 3048}, {\"ngram\": \"a closed gate\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The agency reported that another man needed first-aid after he collapsed.\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3140, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The agency\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3077}, {\"ngram\": \"another man\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3103}, {\"ngram\": \"first-aid\", \"from\": 3111, \"to\": 3120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To add to the woes, heavy rain began when the doors opened at last.\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3209, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the woes\", \"from\": 3152, \"to\": 3160}, {\"ngram\": \"heavy rain\", \"from\": 3162, \"to\": 3172}, {\"ngram\": \"the doors\", \"from\": 3184, \"to\": 3193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Long lines of people were also seen close to the Louvre in central Paris and large crowds also built up close to the start point of the river parade around the Austerlitz bridge, according to the agency.\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3414, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3278, \"end\": 3283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0032141997268009e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3371, \"end\": 3381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_d'Austerlitz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.991362060766822e-17, \"text\": \"Austerlitz\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_d'Austerlitz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_d'Austerlitz\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Long lines\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3221}